text: Candace Kaye Bailey (born May 20, 1982) is an American actress and television host. She is best known as a co-host of the former television programs U-Pick Live on Nickelodeon and Attack of the Show! on G4. ==Other websites== * * Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Birmingham, Alabama Category:American television personalities Category:American television actors
